scenes.description: Moona Hoshinova and Takanashi Kiara perform the song "Majogirl".
Transition scene with a disco ball background and song credits.
Moona Hoshinova and Hololive ID Gen 1 & 2 perform "Etude wa 1 Kyoku Dake".

subtitles.original: ねぇあなたの逃げ場は私 魅惑が引き寄せる
subtitles.english: Hey, I am your refuge, my charm draws you in.

subtitles.original: あの世にあなたの居場所はない ならばしょうがない
subtitles.english: In the next world, you have no place, so it can't be helped.

subtitles.original: 朽ちるまで光りましょう
subtitles.english: Let's shine until we decay,

subtitles.original: ましょう
subtitles.english: shall we?

subtitles.original: はじめましてのキスをしましょう
subtitles.english: Let's have a first-time kiss.

subtitles.original: 何も考えないで 毒々舞う 私の路地
subtitles.english: Don't think about anything, poisonously dancing in my alley.

subtitles.original: まるで運命の糸を結びつける
subtitles.english: It's as if I'm tying the thread of fate.

subtitles.original: お遊び 簡単に騙されて お利口 ほら虜
subtitles.english: Just playing around, easily deceived, such a good boy, see, you're a captive.

subtitles.original: ねぇあなたの逃げ場は私 魅惑が引き寄せる
subtitles.english: Hey, I am your refuge, my charm draws you in.

subtitles.original: あの世にあなたの居場所はない ならばしょうがない
subtitles.english: In the next world, you have no place, so it can't be helped.

subtitles.original: 朽ちるまで光りましょう
subtitles.english: Let's shine until we decay,

subtitles.original: ましょう
subtitles.english: shall we?

subtitles.original: あなたの居場所は私
subtitles.english: I am your place to be.

subtitles.original: あの子にあなたへの愛はない ならばしょうがない
subtitles.english: That girl has no love for you, so it can't be helped.

subtitles.original: 私たち契りましょう 明かしましょう
subtitles.english: Let's make a vow, let's reveal it.

subtitles.original: ねぇあなたの逃げ場は私 魅惑が引き寄せる
subtitles.english: Hey, I am your refuge, my charm draws you in.

subtitles.original: あの世にあなたの居場所はない ならばしょうがない
subtitles.english: In the next world, you have no place, so it can't be helped.

subtitles.original: 朽ちるまで光りましょう
subtitles.english: Let's shine until we decay,

subtitles.original: ましょう
subtitles.english: shall we?

subtitles.original: エチュードは1曲だけ
subtitles.english: Etude wa 1 Kyoku Dake

subtitles.original: カーテン揺らす風が 窓の外からそっと
subtitles.english: The wind shaking the curtains softly from outside the window...

subtitles.original: 教えてくれたのね 出会いの時を
subtitles.english: ...told me about the time of our meeting.

subtitles.original: あなたが弾くピアノは アジサイに軽く歌い
subtitles.english: The piano you play sings lightly to the hydrangeas...

subtitles.original: 立ち止まる私にも ポロポロ 降り注ぐ
subtitles.english: ...and sprinkles down on me as I stop in my tracks.

subtitles.original: 戻れるの
subtitles.english: I can go back,

subtitles.original: 今なら大丈夫さ
subtitles.english: it's okay now.

subtitles.original: 嘘は言わないで 噂の人
subtitles.english: Don't tell lies, you rumored person.

subtitles.original: ノンノン 響いてるわ
subtitles.english: Non-non, it's resonating,

subtitles.original: ギュンギュン ぴゅあなハートに
subtitles.english: gyun-gyun, in my pure heart.

subtitles.original: ダメダメ まだ
subtitles.english: No, no, not yet,

subtitles.original: ダメ 流し目だけは
subtitles.english: no, at least not that sidelong glance.

subtitles.original: ヤンヤン あなたの指が
subtitles.english: Yan-yan, your fingers,

subtitles.original: ダンダン 弾く動き
subtitles.english: dandan, their plucking movements.

subtitles.original: ドキドキ ドキドキ ドキドキ ドキドキ いたずらなエチュード
subtitles.english: Thump-thump, thump-thump... a mischievous etude.

subtitles.original: 大切に過ごしたい 春と夏の真ん中
subtitles.english: I want to spend time carefully, in the middle of spring and summer.

subtitles.original: あの子と同じように 奪われちゃった
subtitles.english: Just like that girl, I've been stolen away.

subtitles.original: 無邪気にハシャぐ声で つま先が彷徨うのよ
subtitles.english: With an innocent, cheerful voice, my toes are wandering.

subtitles.original: ねぇアジサイ 私だけハラハラ 慰めて
subtitles.english: Hey hydrangea, just for me, harahara, comfort me.

subtitles.original: 帰れるの
subtitles.english: I can go home,

subtitles.original: 気にしなくていいさ
subtitles.english: you don't have to worry.

subtitles.original: 曖昧な優しさ 憎たらしい
subtitles.english: Vague kindness is so detestable.

subtitles.original: ノンノン 聴きたくないの
subtitles.english: Non-non, I don't want to hear it,

subtitles.original: ギュンギュン 甘いメロディ
subtitles.english: gyun-gyun, that sweet melody.

subtitles.original: ダメダメ やっぱ
subtitles.english: No, no, as expected, no,

subtitles.original: ダメ 今度はどの子
subtitles.english: which girl is it this time?

subtitles.original: ヤンヤン 待ちぼうけでも
subtitles.english: Yan-yan, even if I'm kept waiting,

subtitles.original: ダンゼン 許してしまう
subtitles.english: I definitely end up forgiving you.

subtitles.original: テテテテ ドキドキ 2人だけエチュード
subtitles.english: Te-te-te-te, thump-thump, an etude for just the two of us.
